Eka ti dyondzo ta [[Ntivo-Ntumbuluko|Fiziksi]], '''Matimba''' mahundziseriwa eka nchumu wokarhi leswaku leswaku matirha –&#x20;&#x6B;&#x75;&#x20;&#x6D;&#x62;&#x65;&#x20;&#x6B;&#x75;&#x20;&#x68;&#x69;&#x73;&#x69;&#x73;&#x61;&#x20;– nchumu wolowo, naswona manga cinciwa muhlovo, kambe matimba ama tumbuluxiwi kumbe ku herisiwa.<ref group="note">The [//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Second_law_of_thermodynamics second law of thermodynamics] can impose limitations on the capacity of a system to transfer energy by performing work, since some of the system's energy might necessarily be [//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Waste_heat "wasted"] in the form of [//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heat heat] instead. </ref> 

Mixakka ya matimba mahlanganisa matimba yo fambisa swilo, matimba lama hlayisiweke hikwalaho ka matshamele ya nchumu wokarhi ekusuhi na matimba yo koka kumbe ya gezi, matimba yo tivuyelela, matimba ya khemikhali lama chunsiwaka loko ku hisiwa mafurha, matimba ya rivoningo na matimba yo kufumeta. 

